home.additionalSources: Additionally, this reference also provides a list of functions available for use when mapping for the Call of Duty 4: Surf Mod as well as new functionality added through CoD4: Unleashed.
home.description: This scripting reference provides information on the different functions available for use in the CoDScript language. To use this information you should be familiar with the basic theory and practice of scripting for one (or more) Call of Duty games (see https://raid-gaming.net/topic/79-beginners-guide-the-index/).
